    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><br><br><h5> This article is reformatted from originally published at <a href="https://towardsdatascience.com/why-python-is-not-the-programming-language-of-the-future-30ddc5339b66"><strong>TDS(Towards Data Science)</strong></a></h5></br><h5> <a href="https://arijoury.medium.com/?source=post_page-----30ddc5339b66--------------------------------">Author : Ari Joury, PhD</a> </h5></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content5 cid-tt5UseJ9wk" id="content5-4" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><h4 class="mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style mb-4 display-7">Opinion</h4></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="content4 cid-tt5SM2WLsM" id="content4-2" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
